acceptOwnership().details: New owner pending to accept ownership executes this function to confirm his ownership.

calculateFee(uint256).details: CalculateFee, given token amount, calculate transfer fee in units/tokens that are cents or pennies

params.tokens: Tokens amount to calculate fees for

getFeesDenominator().details: Get fees as parts per X units

getFeesNumerator().details: Get fees as parts per X units

init(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint256,boo.details: initTransferFees, given all required parameters in the same order as they are declared in the Fee struct.

params._max_Fee: Maximum amount of tokens for the fee, zero means no maximum
params._min_Fee: Mininmum amount of tokens for the fee
params._parts_Fee: Numerator component of the fee percentage
params._perX_Fee: Denominator component of the fee percentage

kill().details: Destroy contract eliminating it from the blockchain

reclaimEther(address).details: Send all eth balance in the contract to another address

params._to: Address to send contract ether balance to

setFees(uint256,uint256).details: Set fees as parts per X units

params._parts_Fee: Parts component of the fee percentage
params._perX_Fee: Per X component of the fee percentage

params.newMaxFee: Maximum amount of tokens to be set as maximum

params.newMinFee: Minimum amount of tokens to be set as minimum

setName(bytes32).details: Change contract name, only admin can do it.

params._newOwner: New owner address acquiring ownership of contract
